{"tid":123450,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"廿到尾三字頭嘅人日常生活應該係點","createTime":"2017-02-17T01:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T05:16:20.000Z","uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e44370fb7eb694f920ca936a33a45ff510efcba","tid":123450,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"做左廿幾年毒撚，係細公司摺左幾年，唔係屋企就公司<br />\n想做返個正常大人，唔指望過幾年即刻三十而立，都想思想行為談吐衣著似大人啲<br />\n<br />\n除左工作技能以外咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 興趣夢想都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再留係呢個空洞嘅comfort zone啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地十幾廿幾去玩去屌閪，點解當時我會摺到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地廿尾三十事業有成結婚生仔，我先想起步行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知要一步一步build up, 巴絲有無好建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真post黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08184a57b8a9db3f69e6d8f3b06c696e6a0702db","tid":123450,"uid":59287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"07928a1f34da28a27a989988fde3a5355dfc48ce","tid":123450,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:21:23.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e70654f1f0b54630eedb5819abdc8befeba03d4","tid":123450,"uid":46726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:23:08.000Z","msg":"搵幾多先?"},{"pid":"4b99e1